The program consists of pieces in editions by me:
1: Keyboard concerto with small orchestra by C. P. E. Bach;
2) Keyboard concerto for two keyboards with string orchestra by C. P. E. Bach;
3) Cantata by J. S. Bach.
vertically, in right margin against above three lines: unpublished works of Bach!end cue
and there might in addition, at my suggestion, be as a fourth work, a concerto by Handel for harp and orchestra.
